channel.title: Private Server Duping Script?
channel.description: Hey could any of you coders out there please create a code that duplicates items on private servers? Because i know it is possible, using some sort of packet editing method. I know of some dupers who play on private servers that say they use SCAR for duping. And if its not true (you [i]cant[/i] duplicate with SCAR) then could you please give me a tutorial on how to packet edit? [b]Any help would be very much appreciated![/b]
